where ğœŒğœŒ is density, ğ‘¡ğ‘¡ is time, ğ’–ğ’– is flow velocity field, ğ‘ğ‘ is pressure, ğ‘°ğ‘° is the identity matrix, ğœ‡ğœ‡ is
